oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Prairie Ramblers - WLS performances - 1941-02-06 // Radio Rogues routine
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Home recorded Prairie Ramblers performances, as performed on February 6, 1941 on radio station WLS (Chicago, IL). Followed by a performance of Two Hearts That Pass In The Night by an unknown performer and a Radio Rogues comedy routine.
